                        Universities use NBT results alongside NSC results for admissions decisions, 
                        student placement, and identifying students who may benefit from additional support. 
                        Each university has its own approach to using NBT results.
                    </p>
                </FluentAccordionItem>

                <FluentAccordionItem Heading="What if a student cannot afford the test fee?">
