                        Some universities and organizations offer bursaries that cover NBT fees for 
                        financially disadvantaged students. Students should inquire at their schools 
                        and chosen universities about available support.
                    </p>
                </FluentAccordionItem>

                <FluentAccordionItem Heading="Can students with disabilities or special needs write the NBT?">
